headline: Parker’s Fiscal Year 2025 Sustainability Report Demonstrates Purpose in Motion
summary: FY25 Sustainability Report Parker Hannifin Corporation CLEVELAND, Feb. 09, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Parker Hannifin Corporation (NYSE: PH), the global leader in motion and control technologies, has released its fiscal year 2025 Sustainability Report.
